title: 01/29/2021 - HOUR 3 - Texans GM Nick Caserio, TJ Houshmandzadeh
itunes:title: 01/29/2021 - HOUR 3 - Texans GM Nick Caserio, TJ Houshmandzadeh
description:
In hour three, Doug breaks down the statement made by Houston Texans GM Nick Caserio that Deshaun Watson will not be traded. TJ Houshmandzadeh joins to give his take on the NFC Championship game and what he thinks will be the case for Green Bay moving forward, with Aaron Rodgers or Jordan Love and more!
